

Extract video frames to lossless PNG
    avconv -i Lewis_Chessmen_Queen_00042.MTS -r 1 -vsync 1 -filter:v "crop=560:740:680:190" -qscale:v 1 -f image2 images/chess-%03d.png

Convert and optmize images


# Sharpened
mogrify -path optimized/ -format jpg -unsharp 0.7x0.7+1+0 -strip -quality 70 ./images/*.png

# Make vertical strip
# +append (top - bottom) -append (left - right)
convert image1.jpg image2.jpg +append output.jpg